}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "UH-404N Rev:1.1" is silkscreened on the board used to populate this entry. Additionally, it is using '''ACON''' ([http://www.acon.com '''Advanced Connectek''']) USB connectors, a '''Wanjia''' WJ102-1C 5V relay, and multiple '''R.K.''' caps (4x 100 μF 16V, 1x 220 μF 16V, 1x 4.7 μF 50V ). :The manufacturer is likely '''Good Way'''.
The '''Genesys Logic''' Hub IC package is marked with "GL650USB" and "0202FCED7-35".
